      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate your <strong>apple[s]</strong> (skin on) and discard the core[s]</p><p>Add your <strong>dried cranberries</strong> to a small bowl and cover with <strong>boiled water</strong>, then set aside to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
