      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build, spread most of the <strong>cranberry mayo </strong>over each <strong>toasted brioche base</strong>, add a <strong>lettuce leaf</strong>, a <strong>pork & apple stuffing patty</strong>, the <strong>parsnip relish </strong>and top with a <strong>toasted brioche lid</strong> – this is your <strong>pork & apple stuffing burger with parsnip relish</strong></p><p>Drizzle the <strong>cranberry</strong> <strong>vinaigrette </strong>over the<strong> lettuce quarters</strong>, then serve the <strong>sage chips</strong> and any <strong>remaining cranberry mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
